    <item>
      <title>中国建筑商远洋集团在伦敦寻求债务计划批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/chinese-builder-sino-ocean-seeks-debt-plan-approval-in-london</link>
      <description><![CDATA[违约的中国建筑商远洋集团控股有限公司将于周三在伦敦一家法院接受为期三天的听证会，寻求行使一项法律机制，允许债务人在未获得债权人完全批准的情况下完成重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/chinese-builder-sino-ocean-seeks-debt-plan-approval-in-london</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:04:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大选前德国 GDP 连续第二年萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/german-economy-shrinks-for-second-straight-year-before-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024年，德国经济连续第二年萎缩，2025年也不太可能大幅增长，这凸显了德国新政府在2月份提前举行选举后面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/german-economy-shrinks-for-second-straight-year-before-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:01:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀缓解市场困境，交易员加大对英国央行降息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示英国12月份通胀率下降后，货币市场纷纷预期英国央行今年将进一步降息，缓解了人们对今年困扰英国资产的持续价格压力的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 07:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际能源署预计今年石油过剩将减少，油价稳定在每桶 80 美元附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯制裁的影响持续显现，且国际能源署 (International Energy Agency) 撤回了对今年的看跌预测，油价基本保持在每桶 80 美元左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 23:31:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
